1. install tomcat
2. go to window -> preference -> runtime env -> server
3. add tomcar 9.0 -> browse the file where it is located in computer C: folder
4. right click on project 
5. run as server
6. add localhost and next and select project and then finish
7. go to winodw -> view perspective -> other -> search server -> click on it
8. see if it is visible in bottom with console
9. check server is stopped , right click and click on open
10. provide the unique port like 8081 or 8082
11. save it
12 run the app again by right click on run as -> server